{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Angel Sign: Dari Komik Bisu, Jadi Film Drama Tingkat Asia","content":"\n<p>Dewasa ini, adaptasi dari satu bentuk hiburan ke bentuk\nhiburan lain sangat marak terjadi. Amerika, Jepang, dan negara-negara lainnya\nramai-ramai membuat franchise hiburan dengan berbagai produk turunannya.\nIndonesia pun merasakan manfaat dari bisnis ini. Tentu masih segar di pikiran\nkita adaptasi film dari komik Gundala yang kini berhasil menyambar lebih dari\n1.5 juta penonton di seluruh negeri dan tayang di festival film bergengsi.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"900\" height=\"506\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4gFDdfZBS7A\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa saja bisa diadaptasi menjadi sesuatu yang baru. Musik\nbisa diadaptasi menjadi film, novel bisa diadaptasi menjadi komik, dan lain\nsebagainya. Nah, di Jepang sendiri ada bentuk adaptasi yang cukup unik, yaitu\nmengubah komik bisu menjadi film drama! Inilah yang akan disajikan dalam film\nAngel Sign.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Angel Sign sendiri merupakan film antologi yang bakal\nmenampilkan berbagai kisah yang digarap oleh sutradara dan aktor berbeda asal\nJepang, Thailand, Vietnam, serta Indonesia. Kebanyakan cerita dalam film ini\ndiadaptasi dari komik bisu karangan peserta kompetisi komik Silent Manga\nAudition. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55764\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/attachment/01-angel-sign/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-angel-sign.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-angel-sign\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-angel-sign-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-angel-sign.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-angel-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Silent Manga Audition\" class=\"wp-image-55764\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-angel-sign.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-angel-sign-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Silent Manga Audition</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kompetisi Silent Manga Audition sendiri diikuti oleh\nberbagai komikus dari seluruh dunia dan telah mencetak puluhan pemenang,\ntermasuk dari Indonesia sendiri yang rutin menempatkan komikusnya sebagai\npenerima penghargaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Film Angel Sign terdiri dari 5 cerita yang diadaptasi dari\nkomik-komik Silent Manga Audition. Cerita-cerita tersebut adalah Beginning and\nFarewell (Anfang und Abschied), Sky Sky, Thirty and a Half Minutes, Father’s\nGift, and Back Home. Selain 5 cerita tersebut, ada juga prolog dan epilog yang\ndisutradarai oleh Tsukasa Hojo.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Biar semakin jelas, inilah sinopsis dari masing-masing segmen dalam film Angel Sign.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/komikus-indonesia-kembali-meraih-penghargaan-silent-manga-audition-8/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Komikus Indonesia Kembali Meraih Penghrgaan Silent Manga Audition 8</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Prologue &amp; Epilogue</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55765\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/attachment/02-angel-sign/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-angel-sign.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-angel-sign\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-angel-sign-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-angel-sign.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-angel-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Prologue &amp; Epilogue. Sumber: akumamoto.jp\" class=\"wp-image-55765\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-angel-sign.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-angel-sign-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Prologue &#038; Epilogue. Sumber: akumamoto.jp</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tsukasa Hojo yang merupakan komikus City Hunter dan juri\nSilent Manga Audition ini menjadi sutradara sekaligus penulis cerita segmen\nprolog dan epilog ini. Bagian ini dibintangi oleh Dean Fujioka dan Nao\nMatsushita. Mereka bermain sebagai pianis Takaya dan cellois Aika, pasangan\nyang bermimpi mengubah dunia lewat musik klasik. Mereka berhasil menciptakan\nkomposisi musik bernama Angel Sign, namun Takaya menghilang tiba-tiba.\nKomposisi musik yang seharusnya dimainkan berdua ini, kini hanya dimainkan\nsendirian oleh Aika.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Beginning and Farewell</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55766\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/attachment/03-angel-sign/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-angel-sign.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-angel-sign\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-angel-sign-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-angel-sign.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-angel-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Beginning &amp; Farewell. Sumber: angelsign.jp\" class=\"wp-image-55766\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-angel-sign.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-angel-sign-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Beginning &#038; Farewell. Sumber: angelsign.jp</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://smacmag.net/v/sma1/beginning-and-ending-by-vincent-lange/517\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Beginning and Farewell (opens in a new tab)\">Beginning and Farewell</a> diadaptasi dari komik bisu Anfang und Abscheid karya Vincent Lange, komikus Jerman yang menjadi runner-up Silent Manga Audition 1. Segmen ini disutradarai oleh Ken Ochiai, dan menampilkan Naoto Ogata serta Momoko Kikuchi sebagai pasangan suami istri yang terpisah oleh maut. Atom, anjing yang dipelihara oleh mereka, berusaha menghibur sang suami yang kini ditinggal istrinya.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sky Sky</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55767\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/attachment/04-angel-sign/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-angel-sign.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-angel-sign\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-angel-sign-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-angel-sign.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-angel-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Sky Sky. Sumber: angelsign.jp\" class=\"wp-image-55767\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-angel-sign.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/04-angel-sign-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sky Sky. Sumber: angelsign.jp</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://smacmag.net/v/sma1/skysky-by-prema-jatukanyaprateep/515\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Sky Sky (opens in a new tab)\">Sky Sky</a> diadaptasi dari komik bisu karya Prema-Ja, komikus Thailand pemenang Silent Manga Audition 1. Segmen ini merupakan produksi Thailand yang disutradarai Nonzee Nimibutr. Dalam segmen ini, seorang anak (Praewpun Parnyim) sulit menerima kenyataan bahwa anjing peliharaannya meninggal karena penyakit. Untuk mengiburnya, ayah (Phiphob Kamolketsophon) dan ibu (Boonin Inlueng) berkata bahwa anjingnya sedang bermain di awan. Anak tersebut kemudian menulis surat dan mengikatnya dengan balon gas agar anjingnya bisa membaca surat tersebut di angkasa.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Thirty and a Half Minutes</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55768\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/attachment/05-angel-sign/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/05-angel-sign.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-angel-sign\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/05-angel-sign-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/05-angel-sign.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/05-angel-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Thirty and a Half Minutes. Sumber: angelsign.jp\" class=\"wp-image-55768\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/05-angel-sign.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/05-angel-sign-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Thirty and a Half Minutes. Sumber: angelsign.jp</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://smacmag.net/v/sma4/thirty-and-a-half-minutes-by-snippy-mj/8286\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Thirty and a Half Minutes (opens in a new tab)\">Thirty and a Half Minutes</a> diadaptasi dari komik bisu karya Snippy MJ, komikus Vietnam pemenang Silent Manga Audition 4. Segmen ini merupakan produksi Vietnam yang disutradarai Han Tran. Pasangan suami istri yang diperankan Ngo Quang Tuan dan Xuan Van ini tengah menanti momongan. Namun takdir berkata lain karena sang istri “disuratkan” untuk meninggal saat persalinan. Merasa iba, malaikat kematian memberikan sebuah kesempatan bagi mereka…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Father’s Gift</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55769\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/attachment/06-angel-sign/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/06-angel-sign.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-angel-sign\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/06-angel-sign-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/06-angel-sign.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/06-angel-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Father’s Gift. Sumber: angelsign.jp\" class=\"wp-image-55769\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/06-angel-sign.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/06-angel-sign-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Father’s Gift. Sumber: angelsign.jp</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://smacmag.net/v/sma2/fathers-gift-by-ichirou/1775\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Father’s Gift (opens in a new tab)\">Father’s Gift</a> diadaptasi dari komik bisu karya Ichirou, komikus Brasil pemenang Silent Manga Audition 2. Segmen ini disutradarai oleh Masatsugu Asahi. Seorang single father (Jiro Sato) berusaha keras mengurus anaknya (Neennara Boonbithipaisit) tanpa figur ibu. Sang ayah kemudian memberikan hadiah robot canggih untuk mengisi peran ibu. Kini sang anak beranjak dewasa (Sayaka Sakai), namun kehilangan semangat hidupnya setelah sang ayah meninggal…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Back Home</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55770\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/angel-sign-silent-manga-audition/attachment/07-angel-sign/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/07-angel-sign.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-angel-sign\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/07-angel-sign-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/07-angel-sign.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/07-angel-sign.jpg\" alt=\"Back Home. Sumber: angelsign.jp\" class=\"wp-image-55770\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/07-angel-sign.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/07-angel-sign-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Back Home. Sumber: angelsign.jp</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Segmen terakhir <a href=\"http://smacmag.net/v/sma4/back-home-by-christ-hazard/8185\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Back Home (opens in a new tab)\">Back Home</a> diadaptasi dari komik bisu karya Vu Dinh Lan, komikus Vietnam runner-up Silent Manga Audition 4. Meskipun merupakan komik bisu dari Vietnam, segmen ini merupakan produksi Indonesia yang disutradarai Kamila Andini dan digarap di Yogyakarta. Seorang ayah (Teuku Rifnu Wikana) hidup tentram bertani di desa bersama anak mereka (Abigail). Ketika perang berkecamuk, sang ayah harus mengangkat senjata dan berjanji akan kembali. Perang telah usai dan sang ayah pun pulang membawa hadiah untuk anaknya yang telah dewasa (Mikako Yoshida). Ketika sampai, sang ayah mendapatkan sebuah kejutan yang tak terduga.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Angel Sign akan tayang di Jepang mulai tanggal 15 November.\nMengingat ada segmen yang diproduksi di Yogyakarta, apakah film ini juga bakal\ntayang di Indonesia ya?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"dcb1c591-9417-5f74-9938-9ff37239888b"}}}